1
00:00:03,179 --> 00:00:04,873
My name is Philip.

2
00:00:04,960 --> 00:00:05,960
Hello.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:07,000
Sorry.

4
00:00:07,533 --> 00:00:09,720
The witch has demanded a meeting with
Aslan!

5
00:00:10,780 --> 00:00:12,400
The queen of Blania!

6
00:00:12,820 --> 00:00:13,820
Go away!

7
00:00:13,960 --> 00:00:16,400
Emperors of Long Island!

8
00:00:27,353 --> 00:00:29,760
You have a traitor in your midst,
Aslan.

9
00:00:30,386 --> 00:00:32,800
His offence was not against you.

10
00:00:33,680 --> 00:00:36,860
Have you forgotten the laws upon which
Narnia was built?

11
00:00:37,040 --> 00:00:39,760
Do not cite the deep magic to me,
witch.

12
00:00:40,653 --> 00:00:42,440
I was there when it was written.

13
00:00:44,780 --> 00:00:48,660
Then you'll remember well that every
traitor belongs to me.

14
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:52,173
His blood is my property.

15
00:00:53,220 --> 00:00:54,140
Try and take him, then.

